    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required gradation levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at Gradation 1 for MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Experimental validation confirms RH < 1 at all 5 operating points with maximum error 14.1%, within the 15% acceptance criterion. The UQ campaign (documented in ValidationResult narratives) confirmed robustness of hemolysis predictions across the manufacturing tolerance envelope. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
